  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>We have included a full range of daytime arctic activities, including carefully selected husky, reindeer and snowmobile safaris. Guests can also enjoy these special surroundings by snowshoe or cross-country skis on a network of over 300 kms of prepared trails. On included evening aurora hunts, expert local guides will take you in search of the <a data-udi="umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271" href="/{localLink:umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a> by minibus, snowmobile or snowmobile-pulled sled.</p>
<p>The lodge owners, Jouko and Mari, and their very friendly staff, have years of expertise in arranging holidays in locations that are specifically designed to provide guests with the best possible opportunities for witnessing the magical Northern Lights.</p>
<h2>What's Included</h2>
<ul>
<li>Inghams REP based in Saariselkä. </li>
<li>Non-stop flights from Gatwick, Manchester or Bristol on Sundays to Kittilä for 7 night holidays.</li>
<li>Scenic airport coach transfers.</li>
<li>Full board meals at Muotka Lodge.</li>
<li>Half board meals at Gielas Hotel or Holiday Club Hotel in Saariselkä on 2-Centre holidays.</li>
<li>Aurora Alert until approx. 1am.</li>
<li>Safety briefing and instruction from experienced Muotka safari guides.</li>
<li>Warm thermal clothing and boots.</li>
<li>Third party snowmobile insurance (insurance excess approx €800).</li>
<li>Free use of snowshoe and cross-country ski equipment for whole stay after taking an included guided trip.</li>
<li>Activities as listed in the itineraries including snowmobile, reindeer and husky safaris, guided snowshoe and cross-country ski trips, evening Aurora Northern Lights hunting excursion</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Stay in an Aurora Cabin Overnight </strong></p>
<p>The ultimate experience for many guests is a night in an Aurora Cabin with a north-facing glass roof window, perfect for lying in bed and gazing up a the night sky. A special pre-bookable upgrade price of £99 per person if staying in a Lodge Room (£195 for single occupancy), or £59 per person if staying in a Superior Room with Sauna or Log Cabin, is available to Inghams guests on all dates. </p>
<p>The Aurora Cabin overnight must be pre-booked and the exact night is subject to change locally. </p>
<div class="g12"><img src="/media/13050672/aurora-cabin-holiday-type.jpg" alt="Overnight in an Aurora Cabin" rel="858,410" /></div>
<h3><strong>Holiday Choice</strong></h3>
<p>We offer Inghams guests a choice of two types of Northern Lights themed holidays - either all <a data-udi="umb://document/6fc20d9f96544a77815dae85486b19a2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6fc20d9f96544a77815dae85486b19a2}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure">7 nights</a> at <a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Muotka Wilderness Lodge</a> or a week with the first 4 nights at <a data-udi="umb://document/3f5398805f5841a28e1f5829945f8748" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f5398805f5841a28e1f5829945f8748}" title="Tunturi Hotel / Gielas Hotel">Gielas Hotel</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2}" title="Holiday Club Spa Hotel">Holiday Club Hotel</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a>, followed by <a data-udi="umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714}" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure">3 nights</a> at Muotka.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="height: 400px;"><img src="/media/13050677/muotka-lodge-holiday-type.jpg?width=504&amp;height=241" alt="Muotka Wilderness Lodge" width="504" height="241" rel="858,410" />
<h2>Muotka 7 Night Adventure</h2>
<p>Spend 7 nights in Muotka, near Saariselkä as part of our Northern Lights Adventure Weeks.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6fc20d9f96544a77815dae85486b19a2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6fc20d9f96544a77815dae85486b19a2}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure">More information</a></p>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="height: 400px;"><img src="/media/13050674/gielas-holiday-type.jpg?width=509&amp;height=243" alt="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure" width="509" height="243" rel="858,410" />
<h2>Muotka 2-Centre Adventure</h2>
<p>Spend 4 nights in Saariselkä and 3 nights in Muotka, near Saariselkä as part of our Northern Lights Adventure Weeks.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714}" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure">More information</a></p>
