  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>Muotka Wilderness Lodge is a lovingly renovated family-run property set in a secluded snow-laden winter wonderland, 15 kms from Saariselkä village. Its idyllic location on the edge of the pristine Urho-Kekkonen National Park guarantees minimal light pollution and therefore an increased potential for seeing the Northern Lights, simply by stepping outside the lodge’s front door. Guests can be as active as they choose in this totally relaxing stress-free environment.</p>]]></shortDescription>
